00:04:27,750 --> 00:04:29,000
REALLY DO EXIST.

52
00:04:29,083 --> 00:04:32,416
- BUT I WONDER
WHO THE CLUB'S PRESIDENT IS.

53
00:04:32,500 --> 00:04:34,291
- IF THEY CAME ALL THE WAY HERE,

54
00:04:34,375 --> 00:04:36,958
