AND TAKE A DEEP BREATH.

113
00:07:22,125 --> 00:07:25,375
GOT IT NOW?
- ACTUALLY, CHIKA-CHAN--

114
00:07:25,458 --> 00:07:27,916
- BOING, SPLISH-SPLASH
AND HUFF-PUFF?

115
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:30,375
