JUST MAKING SOUND EFFECTS?

116
00:07:30,458 --> 00:07:33,833
- OH, YEAH, I GUESS
YOU'RE RIGHT. ( laughs )

117
00:07:33,916 --> 00:07:36,208
- LISTEN, CHIZURU,
THE REASON THAT YOU'RE NOT

118
00:07:36,291 --> 00:07:37,583
