131
00:08:06,041 --> 00:08:08,583
- READY, CHIZURU?
- I'M READY, COACH.

132
00:08:08,666 --> 00:08:09,541
- HUH?

133
00:08:19,916 --> 00:08:22,291
- SEE?
WASN'T THAT EASY?  HUH?

134
00:08:22,375 --> 00:08:25,208
- ( gasps )
- ( whimpers )

135
00:08:26,791 --> 00:08:28,625
- CHIZURU, HANG ON!

136
00:08:33,166 --> 00:08:36,708
- NOW THAT I THINK ABOUT IT,
YOU AND I CAN SWIM, BUT--

137
00:08:36,791 --> 00:08:38,875
- SWIMMING AND TEACHING
SOMEONE HOW TO SWIM

138
00:08:38,958 --> 00:08:40,875
ARE TWO DIFFERENT THINGS.

