AND FASTEST SOLUTION.

142
00:08:48,458 --> 00:08:51,208
BUT OUR SWIMMING CLUB
DOESN'T HAVE A COACH.

143
00:08:52,291 --> 00:08:54,333
- OH!  IN THAT CASE,

144
00:08:54,416 --> 00:08:56,958
ALL WE HAVE TO DO IS
ASK SOMEONE TO BE OUR COACH!

145
00:08:57,041 --> 00:08:59,000
PROBLEM SOLVED!
- THEN YOU'VE GOTTA HAVE

146
00:08:59,083 --> 00:09:01,458
SOMEONE IN MIND WHO CAN BE
OUR COACH, RIGHT, CHIKA?

147
00:09:01,541 --> 00:09:03,416
- HM-MMM.  NOPE.

148
00:09:03,500 --> 00:09:04,875
