176
00:10:09,625 --> 00:10:11,625
- YOU'RE INCREDIBLE, MS. TINA!

177
00:10:11,708 --> 00:10:13,916
- NOW DON'T WORRY ABOUT A THING.

178
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:15,125
WITH ME AS YOUR COACH,

179
00:10:15,208 --> 00:10:16,958
