- ( grunting )

184
00:10:34,666 --> 00:10:38,250
- OKAY, THAT'S IT FOR THE
WARM-UP DRILL! GATHER AROUND.

185
00:10:38,333 --> 00:10:40,916
THERE ISN'T MUCH TIME
UNTIL THE COMPETITION,

186
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:43,000
SO I'M NOT GONNA
TAKE IT EASY, OKAY?

187
00:10:43,083 --> 00:10:44,708
YOU GUYS BETTER
BE READY FOR THIS.

188
00:10:44,791 --> 00:10:47,416
- RIGHT!
- THERE'S JUST ONE THING.

189
00:10:47,500 --> 00:10:49,000
BEFORE WE START YOUR TRAINING,

190
00:10:49,083 --> 00:10:52,333
THERE'S ONE VERY IMPORTANT THING
THAT CAN'T BE AVOIDED.

191
00:10:52,416 --> 00:10:54,375
- ( all gulp )
- AND THAT IS...

192
00:10:54,458 --> 00:10:55,833
