198
00:11:06,083 --> 00:11:08,375
ALL RIGHT,
NEXT UP IS CHIKA!

199
00:11:08,458 --> 00:11:09,708
- OKAY.

200
00:11:09,791 --> 00:11:12,291
- WHOO! YOU'RE DEFINITELY TAE'S
COUSIN ALL RIGHT.

201
00:11:12,375 --> 00:11:14,416
