TO RUSH THINGS.

219
00:12:47,875 --> 00:12:51,791
- ( whistle tweets )
- TODAY'S PRACTICE IS OVER!

220
00:12:51,875 --> 00:12:54,458
- CHIZURU-CHAN, LET'S GO.

221
00:12:54,541 --> 00:12:57,041
- GO ON... AHEAD.

222
00:12:57,125 --> 00:13:00,416
