NEXT WEEK

226
00:13:10,125 --> 00:13:12,083
AND I UNDERSTAND
WHY YOU WANNA RUSH,

227
00:13:12,166 --> 00:13:15,125
BUT IF YOU PUSH TOO HARD,
YOU'LL NEVER GET BETTER.

228
00:13:15,208 --> 00:13:17,666
- UM, THAT'S NOT IT.

229
00:13:17,750 --> 00:13:19,000
- HUH?

230
00:13:19,083 --> 00:13:21,458
- IT'S NOT BECAUSE OF THE
COMPETITION OR ANYTHING.

231
00:13:21,541 --> 00:13:23,833
IT'S BECAUSE I DECIDED

232
00:13:23,916 --> 00:13:25,708
THAT BEFORE THE END
OF THE SUMMER

233
00:13:25,791 --> 00:13:28,375
I'D BE ABLE TO SWIM 25 METERS
NO MATTER WHAT.

234
00:13:29,750 --> 00:13:32,500
THAT'S WHY I WANT
TO SWIM THOSE 25 METERS--

235
00:13:32,583 --> 00:13:34,958
NOT FOR THE COMPETITION
BUT FOR MYSELF.

236
00:13:35,041 --> 00:13:36,875
AFTER ALL, I WANT
TO BE ABLE TO SWIM

237
00:13:36,958 --> 00:13:38,916
WITH CHIKA-CHAN
AND NATSUKI-CHAN.

238
00:13:43,083 --> 00:13:46,041
I UNDERSTAND, AND THE
SUMMER'S NOT OVER JUST YET.

239
00:13:46,125 --> 00:13:49,000
LET'S DO THE BEST WE CAN
TILL THE VERY VERY END

240
00:13:49,083 --> 00:13:50,750
AND LET'S MAKE
THE GREATEST MEMORIES!

241
00:13:50,833 --> 00:13:52,833
- MS. TINA.

242
00:13:52,916 --> 00:13:55,666
- ALL RIGHT, THE EXTRA
TRAINING TIME STARTS NOW!

243
00:13:55,750 --> 00:13:58,333
- I LEAVE MYSELF
IN YOUR CAPABLE HANDS, COACH.

244
00:13:58,416 --> 00:14:01,083
- HEY, YOU'RE BENDING
YOUR KNEES AGAIN.

245
00:14:01,166 --> 00:14:03,625
- UNDERSTOOD, COACH.
- STRAIGHTEN YOUR BACK!

246
00:14:03,708 --> 00:14:05,083
- RIGHT.

247
00:14:06,833 --> 00:14:08,750
- ( jazz music playing )

248
00:15:07,666 --> 00:15:10,583
- CAN I HAVE A MISO PORK
CUTLET BURGER, FRIES

249
00:15:10,666 --> 00:15:12,708
AND AN ORANGE SODA PLEASE?

250
00:15:17,000 --> 00:15:18,041
YOU KNOW...

251
00:15:19,333 --> 00:15:21,750
THERE'S NOTHING
MORE SATISFYING IN THE WORLD...

252
00:15:21,833 --> 00:15:24,291
THAN A NICE MEAL
AFTER A HARD WORKOUT.

253
00:15:25,541 --> 00:15:27,750
HMM?  I'M PAYING
FOR EVERYTHING,

254
00:15:27,833 --> 00:15:30,625
SO WHY DON'T YOU STOP HOLDING
BACK AND EAT UP ALREADY, OKAY?

255
00:15:30,708 --> 00:15:33,500
- THANKS A LOT
FOR THE FOOD, COACH.

256
00:15:36,041 --> 00:15:37,708
- OH, BY THE WAY,
I THINK I SAW--

257
00:15:37,791 --> 00:15:39,666
- I'M JEALOUS.
- HUH?

258
00:15:39,750 --> 00:15:42,750
- HUH?  I WAS
JUST THINKING TO MYSELF

259
00:15:42,833 --> 00:15:45,416
THAT I WISH I COULD'VE SPENT MY
HIGH SCHOOL YEARS HERE IN JAPAN.

260
00:15:45,500 --> 00:15:48,583
IT'D BE LIKE
THE UNIFORM AND ALL.

261
00:15:48,666 --> 00:15:49,833
I THINK THEY'RE CUTE.

262
00:15:49,916 --> 00:15:53,750
AND I KINDA LIKE BEING
JUST LIKE EVERYONE ELSE.

263
00:15:53,833 --> 00:15:55,250
FITTING IN, YOU KNOW?

264
00:15:57,791 --> 00:16:00,500
IF I HAD GONE
TO A JAPANESE HIGH SCHOOL,

265
00:16:00,583 --> 00:16:02,541
WOULD THIS BE
WHAT IT FEELS LIKE?

266
00:16:02,625 --> 00:16:06,583
I WONDER IF I WOULD'VE HAD
FUN TIMES LIKE RIGHT NOW.

267
00:16:06,666 --> 00:16:08,708
- UM, MS. TINA?

268
00:16:16,333 --> 00:16:18,208
- ( crowd cheering )

269
00:16:29,083 --> 00:16:32,833
- WHAT?  THAT TARZAN WOMAN
IS THEIR SWIMMING COACH?

270
00:16:32,916 --> 00:16:35,458
ARE YOU SURE THEY'LL BE FINE,
HANABISHI-SAMA?

271
00:16:35,541 --> 00:16:37,500
- YEAH, THEY'VE ALL GOTTEN
SO MUCH FASTER

272
00:16:37,583 --> 00:16:39,208
AT SWIMMING
AND IT'S REALLY NOTICEABLE.

273
00:16:39,291 --> 00:16:40,791
- LADY AOI?

274
00:16:40,875 --> 00:16:43,208
MS. CHIKA AND THE OTHERS
WILL BE GOING SOON.

275
00:16:46,000 --> 00:16:48,583
- NATSUKI, CHIZURU, CHIKA.

276
00:16:48,666 --> 00:16:50,458
WE'LL BE GOING
WITH THIS ORDER.

277
00:16:50,541 --> 00:16:52,833
THERE'S NOTHING LEFT
FOR ME TO TEACH YOU.

278
00:16:52,916 --> 00:16:54,958
ALL THAT'S LEFT IS
TO GIVE IT EVERYTHING

279
00:16:55,041 --> 00:16:56,750
AND MAKE SURE YOU
HAVE NO REGRETS.

280
00:16:56,833 --> 00:16:57,833
- OKAY!

281
00:16:57,916 --> 00:16:59,083
- BUT IN THE END,

282
00:16:59,166 --> 00:17:02,125
I NEVER MANAGED TO SWIM 25
METERS EVEN ONCE.

283
00:17:02,208 --> 00:17:05,541
- LET'S DO OUR BEST,
CHIZURU-CHAN.

284
00:17:08,416 --> 00:17:10,541
- YES, LET'S DO OUR BEST.

285
00:17:10,625 --> 00:17:14,166
- We will now begin
the girls' 25-meter relay.

286
00:17:14,250 --> 00:17:16,125
Starters,
please take your mark.

287
00:17:16,208 --> 00:17:18,000
- ( cheering )

288
00:17:18,083 --> 00:17:20,041
- OH, I CAN SEE THEM.

289
00:17:20,125 --> 00:17:22,625
- CHIKA-CHAN!
- WHERE?  WHERE?

290
00:17:33,125 --> 00:17:34,583
- I'LL DO MY BEST.

291
00:17:34,666 --> 00:17:36,583
- COME ON, YOU CAN DO IT!

292
00:17:36,666 --> 00:17:38,500
- ON YOUR MARKS,

293
00:17:38,583 --> 00:17:40,500
GET SET...

294
00:17:40,583 --> 00:17:42,000
- ALL RIGHT,

295
00:17:42,083 --> 00:17:44,500
I'M GONNA MAKE SURE TO TAKE
THE LEAD ON THE FIRST PASS.

296
00:17:44,583 --> 00:17:45,791
- ( gunshot )
- ( grunts )

297
00:17:49,208 --> 00:17:51,125
- ( cheering )

298
00:17:56,791 --> 00:17:58,083
- GO, NATSUKI!

299
00:17:58,166 --> 00:17:59,541
BLOW 'EM AWAY!

300
00:17:59,625 --> 00:18:02,583
- LOOK AT THAT.
- WHERE?  WHERE?

301
00:18:02,666 --> 00:18:05,250
- CHIZURU, GO!

302
00:18:05,333 --> 00:18:07,666
- UH, WAIT.
( screams )

303
00:18:10,083 --> 00:18:12,791
- HUH?
- THAT LOOKED PAINFUL.

304
00:18:21,333 --> 00:18:25,125
- OH NO, THE OTHERS
HAVE MANAGED TO PASS HER.

305
00:18:25,208 --> 00:18:26,958
( gasps )
AND AGAIN.

306
00:18:27,041 --> 00:18:28,458
CHIZURU!

307
00:18:28,541 --> 00:18:29,791
GIVE IT YOUR ALL!

308
00:18:29,875 --> 00:18:32,708
- ( woman laughs )
WHAT'S WITH THAT GIRL?

309
00:18:32,791 --> 00:18:35,291
- HOW DID SOMEONE AS SLOW
AS HER GET INTO THIS RELAY?

310
00:18:35,375 --> 00:18:37,833
- OH MAN, IS SHE FOR REAL?

311
00:18:37,916 --> 00:18:38,958
- ( scoffs )

312
00:18:39,041 --> 00:18:42,166
- SILENCE! SILENCE,
SILENCE, SILENCE!

313
00:18:42,250 --> 00:18:43,791
- MS. CHIZURU!

314
00:18:43,875 --> 00:18:45,625
DO YOU BEST OUT THERE!

315
00:18:45,708 --> 00:18:47,833
- GO FOR BROKE,
CHIZURU-CHAN!

316
00:18:49,458 --> 00:18:50,916
- I CAN'T LOSE.

317
00:18:51,000 --> 00:18:53,458
AFTER ALL,
I DECIDED FOR MYSELF

318
00:18:53,541 --> 00:18:55,541
THAT I'D SWIM 25 METERS.

319
00:19:01,666 --> 00:19:04,458
I WILL BE ABLE
TO SWIM THAT DISTANCE

320
00:19:04,541 --> 00:19:07,791
BEFORE THE SUMMER... ENDS.

321
00:19:07,875 --> 00:19:10,333
I WILL BE ABLE

322
00:19:10,416 --> 00:19:13,333
TO SWIM WITH MY FRIENDS.

323
00:19:13,416 --> 00:19:16,750
I WILL, I WILL, I WILL!

324
00:19:20,208 --> 00:19:21,833
- ALL RIGHT!
- CHIZURU!

325
00:19:21,916 --> 00:19:23,541
- YOU DID IT,
CHIZURU-CHAN!

326
00:19:29,375 --> 00:19:31,916
HERE I GO!

327
00:19:37,416 --> 00:19:39,708
CHIZURU-CHAN WORKED SO HARD,

328
00:19:39,791 --> 00:19:41,958
I CAN'T LET US LOSE!

329
00:19:43,291 --> 00:19:44,791
- LOOK, KAORU-SAMA.
- YEAH.

330
00:19:44,875 --> 00:19:46,875
IT LOOKS LIKE CHIKA-CHAN
JUST MIGHT MAKE IT.

331
00:19:46,958 --> 00:19:49,083
CHIKA-CHAN,
YOU CAN DO IT!

332
00:19:51,500 --> 00:19:54,375
- ( yelling )

333
00:19:54,458 --> 00:19:56,375
- ( crowd roars )

334
00:20:03,416 --> 00:20:04,875
- THAT'S TOO BAD.

335
00:20:04,958 --> 00:20:06,666
JUST A BIT MORE
AND WE WOULD'VE WON.

336
00:20:06,750 --> 00:20:09,083
- ( laughs )
EXCEPT MY LEG CRAMPED UP,

337
00:20:09,166 --> 00:20:11,916
SO IT'S ALL MY FAULT THAT OUR
TEAM ENDED UP IN LAST PLACE.

338
00:20:12,000 --> 00:20:13,708
- ARE YOU ALL RIGHT,
CHIKA-CHAN?

339
00:20:13,791 --> 00:20:16,250
- BUT YOU KNOW, YOU REALLY
DID YOUR BEST, CHIZURU.

340
00:20:16,333 --> 00:20:20,291
- NOT AT ALL.
- YEAH, REALLY DID WORK HARD.

341
00:20:20,375 --> 00:20:23,416
YOU DID A GREAT JOB AT
SWIMMING THOSE 25 METERS,

342
00:20:23,500 --> 00:20:25,083
YOU LITTLE TUNA GIRL.

343
00:20:25,166 --> 00:20:27,458
- OH, BUT THIS IS
ALL THANKS TO YOU, COACH.

344
00:20:27,541 --> 00:20:30,875
- HM-MMM. THIS HAPPENED
BECAUSE OF ALL YOUR EFFORT.

345
00:20:30,958 --> 00:20:33,791
- MS. TINA.
- OKAY, THEN TO CELEBRATE

346
00:20:33,875 --> 00:20:35,958
YOU REACHING YOUR GOAL...
- HUH?

347
00:20:36,041 --> 00:20:39,375
- ...IT'S TIME FOR YOUR
BREAST CHECK, CHIZURU!

348
00:20:39,458 --> 00:20:41,833
- WHOO-HOO!
YOU MAY BE A SMALL FRY

349
00:20:41,916 --> 00:20:43,916
AND DEAD LAST
WHEN IT COMES TO SWIMMING,

350
00:20:44,000 --> 00:20:46,416
BUT YOU'RE FIRST
WHEN IT COMES TO BOOBIES!

351
00:20:46,500 --> 00:20:49,916
- HEY, YOU GUYS!
- OH, IT'S CHIKA'S BOYFRIEND.

352
00:20:50,000 --> 00:20:52,416
- I TOLD YOU BEFORE,
HE'S NOT.  OW!

353
00:20:52,500 --> 00:20:55,416
- ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?
- PLEASE DON'T PUSH YOURSELF.

354
00:20:55,500 --> 00:20:57,125
IS YOUR LEG OKAY,
CHIKA-CHAN?

355
00:20:57,208 --> 00:20:57,666
- YEAH.

356
00:20:57,750 --> 00:20:59,500
- ( chattering )

357
00:21:02,875 --> 00:21:06,750
- WELL, IT LOOKS LIKE I'VE MADE
YET ANOTHER PRECIOUS MEMORY.

358
00:21:14,333 --> 00:21:16,291
I NEED TO MAKE EVEN MORE.

359
00:21:16,375 --> 00:21:19,000
MORE HAPPY MEMORIES
WITH EVERYONE.

360
00:21:29,291 --> 00:21:31,791
IT'S ALREADY AUTUMN,
ISN'T IT?

361
00:21:36,250 --> 00:21:38,333
- ( theme music playing )

362
00:21:38,416 --> 00:21:40,333
( singing in Japanese )

363
00:23:08,166 --> 00:23:11,875
- WHERE EXACTLY CAN
KAORU-SAMA'S HAPPINESS BE FOUND?

364
00:23:11,958 --> 00:23:15,166
MY HAPPINESS IS RIGHT HERE.

365
00:23:15,250 --> 00:23:17,083
WHEN I CAN'T SEE HIM,

366
00:23:17,166 --> 00:23:18,666
AND WHEN I'M WITH HIM--

367
00:23:18,750 --> 00:23:21,666
MY HAPPINESS, YES,

368
00:23:21,750 --> 00:23:24,500
IS WITHIN KAORU-SAMA.

369
00:23:24,583 --> 00:23:29,166
ON THE NEXT EPISODE OF "AI
YORI AOSHI: ENISHI," "WHITE."

370
00:23:29,250 --> 00:23:31,750
WHEN I THINK OF KAORU-SAMA,

371
00:23:31,833 --> 00:23:35,500
THAT ALONE IS ENOUGH
TO MAKE ME HAPPY.

